@deftypefun int gcry_cipher_encrypt (GCRY_CIPHER_HD @var{h}, unsigned char *{out}, size_t @var{outsize}, const unsigned char *@var{in}, size_t @var{inlen})

@code{gcry_cipher_encrypt} is used to encrypt the data.
